Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.17,0:00:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.44,0:00:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.08,0:00:26.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.61,0:00:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.49,0:00:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.09,0:00:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.17,0:00:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.74,0:00:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.27,0:00:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.88,0:01:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.32,0:01:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.82,0:01:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.45,0:01:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.79,0:01:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.32,0:01:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.83,0:01:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.80,0:01:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C. 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.22,0:01:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,侵入者嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.69,0:01:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,病毒侵入防壁 感染擴大中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.86,0:01:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抗體發生機能衝突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.46,0:01:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵方的掃瞄突破外壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.27,0:01:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,增加外圍防衛線分配的資源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.47,0:01:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感染部位用誘餌應付後廢棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,病毒分析狀況 互相侵蝕進行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.21,0:02:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,14種中和 2種進行中 1種未特定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.58,0:02:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼叫作未特定?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.15,0:02:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點確認
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.98,0:02:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初見為無活性 無反應可能是誘餌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.85,0:02:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改變抗體的版本後繼續分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要被敵人看穿應對手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.35,0:02:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人開始控制中繼器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法以物理方式切斷回路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.03,0:02:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,— 可惡 — 侵入的病毒開始增殖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.73,0:02:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是哪來的電賊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.96,0:02:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一防衛線60%消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向波賽頓的十手巨人申請支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.03,0:02:25.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十手巨人：波賽頓工業的巨型終端名\N詞源出自希臘神話中的百手百足巨人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.20,0:02:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#09 名為絕望的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是晚了一步嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.43,0:02:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.53,0:02:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必須先救出傷患
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.03,0:03:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請快派救護車過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.37,0:03:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地點是新濱3區購物廣場 需要五輛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.95,0:03:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一模一樣 不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.72,0:03:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自殺炸彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.49,0:03:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使用混入螺絲釘的C-4塑膠炸彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.43,0:03:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.46,0:03:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無差別恐怖攻擊 還發出預告這到底算什麼東西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.97,0:03:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看樣子恐怖的規模本身才是這傢伙的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.90,0:03:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怖的規模
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.31,0:03:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟「個別的11人」一樣事先發出犯罪預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.81,0:03:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果卻反覆犯下無差別自殺炸彈攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.08,0:03:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這很明顯是那種從行為本身尋找行動意義的麻煩類型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.45,0:03:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 你認為這次自殺炸彈攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少還會再發生一次?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.12,0:03:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果相信犯罪預告的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.66,0:04:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個國家到底怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.93,0:04:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是哪方面開始瘋狂了呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就算有多少分身都不夠用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長 這樣根本追不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.91,0:04:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯罪預告裏面找不到關於時間或地點的暗示嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.18,0:04:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前縣警只接到一封郵件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.12,0:04:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫著「今天新濱市內將發生五起自殺炸彈攻擊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.52,0:04:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果跟上禮拜福岡那邊發生的案件類型相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.89,0:04:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一件也一定會在新濱這裏發生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.73,0:04:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們把現場交給縣警處理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何一定要阻止下一次的爆炸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.27,0:04:45.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使要把新濱市內做過義體化的人全部抓起來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.21,0:04:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說是無差別恐怖攻擊應該也有某種方向性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.11,0:04:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.01,0:04:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來 這麼忙的時候少校那傢伙跑哪去了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說去做極機密的潛入調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,極機密嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.85,0:05:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏交給管區和兩位老先生我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波瑪 找到什麼線索就跟我聯絡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.63,0:05:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種自殺炸彈攻擊到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是外來統治下的無政府國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.44,0:05:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這表示這個國家也已經不像嘴巴上說的那麼和平了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.61,0:05:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確 難民問題是個何時引爆都不奇怪的火藥庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.25,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個人主義者會這麼激進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.28,0:05:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前景令人不安的國政或許也要負點責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.19,0:05:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我竟然忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有難民這個可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.09,0:05:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.33,0:05:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上周福岡發生的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.26,0:05:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有這幾小時內發生的自殺炸彈攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.83,0:05:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩調查一下這兩者的嫌疑犯是什麼樣的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.87,0:05:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屍體幾乎都面目全非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.44,0:05:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯一知道的就是義體化率比較高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.85,0:06:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,IR系統或監視攝影機應該有拍到他們生前的模樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想請你把這些影像都收集起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.59,0:06:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.85,0:06:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我試試看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種案件呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.86,0:06:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是有人強迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.63,0:06:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者上面下命令就能這樣大規模發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.93,0:06:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂自殺炸彈攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.57,0:06:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是人在沒有任何活下去的希望時才會去幹的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長 沒問題吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像相當被動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.90,0:06:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次一定會控制住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.53,0:06:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那邊狀況怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.50,0:06:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬代理化之後狀況良好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.27,0:07:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幾乎不必考慮距離上的損耗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.54,0:07:04.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然贏不了 不過也不會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.35,0:07:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要做得太過火喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.88,0:07:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就要看狀況了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.95,0:07:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之 我會自我約束的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全感覺遮罩還在作用中嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最短路徑搜尋完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.73,0:07:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遮罩陣列啟動完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.73,0:07:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保全室緊急防護鎖解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.75,0:07:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,— 敵方攻性防壁512種 — 合體型病毒進行中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.15,0:07:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,— 在第一級展開中 — 現在進行率52％
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,— 403為破壞移動型 — 防衛線70％恢復
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,— 82為合體部品 — 22％交戰中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.92,0:07:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,— 27為炸彈和誘餌 — 8％被侵蝕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.96,0:07:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,— 來自十手巨人的支援防壁 — 敵方512種攻性防壁中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.06,0:07:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,— 最大機能達到97％ — 7種侵入第二級 要求誘餌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.36,0:07:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,— 復原了嗎? — 敵方403種攻性防壁中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.00,0:07:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,108種消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.47,0:08:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都交給AI的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隨便阿貓阿狗都能快你一步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電警有報告進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.38,0:08:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從案件發生地點回收的影像中
