Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.66,0:09:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是一般國民這邊對他們更不滿才對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正因為如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.67,0:09:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別的11人這種個別主義者才會漸漸抬頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.84,0:09:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對此的反彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.51,0:09:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真要說起來可以算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.88,0:09:57.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概可以認為難民這個火藥庫已經被點上火了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.95,0:10:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不惜自殺也要提出某種訴求
