Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一件應該會隔得更遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連續自殺炸彈攻擊時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.32,0:10:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先覺悟的傢伙會先去實行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.46,0:10:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到下次自爆之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.92,0:10:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信還有一些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老大 對這種棘手的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還真是清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以順便問你一個問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.14,0:10:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼問題?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.18,0:10:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果目的在於恐怖的大小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.51,0:11:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不發出爆炸預告就實行我認為效果會更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.12,0:11:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認為那些傢伙當初為何要發出預告?
