Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.89,0:11:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是希望讓世界上有人知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.42,0:11:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己所做的最後行動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.10,0:11:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如我所料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然從合田的經歷上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早就確定他跟波賽頓關係很深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.97,0:11:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過沒想到會這麼制度化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.48,0:11:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陷阱嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.31,0:11:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,路由陣列3軸展開
