Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.15,0:12:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 把所有感覺系統投入最厚的防壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.39,0:12:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在敵人到之前
