Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有機能衝突
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.00,0:12:58.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 以保安部員凍結狀態被發現為界限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.07,0:13:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們負責監視45個電子腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.60,0:13:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現有狀況馬上通知我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.74,0:13:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.01,0:13:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.50,0:13:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是傳說中的十手巨人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.50,0:13:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以大量資料為基礎構築虛擬人格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不斷做模擬測試嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是合田一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.71,0:13:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前在大日本技研從事除去放射能粉塵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.15,0:13:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,分子工學機械人計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除去放射能粉塵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.42,0:13:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是指日本的奇跡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.63,0:13:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擔任技術人員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.29,0:14:00.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.59,0:14:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我腦部的語言機能經過特殊化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.60,0:14:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,歷經兩次大戰之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.83,0:14:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,利用我領導設計出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.67,0:14:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放射能除去技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.34,0:14:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個國家再度成為經濟大國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.31,0:14:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在那時候原本也應該進入人類的最上層構造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是就像這個國家在國際社會中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.78,0:14:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無法獲得什麼崇高地位一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.75,0:14:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在社會系統當中也無法佔有重要的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.82,0:14:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的意思是社會不給只動嘴的人太高的評價嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.40,0:14:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很久以前就發現目前的社會系統上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.80,0:14:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有構造性的致命缺陷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.08,0:14:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原本應該不會變質的情報變質了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.51,0:14:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有名為「個性」的虛幻原創性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.02,0:15:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在現在的社會系統內很簡單就會發生同步化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.52,0:15:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把這個現象稱為「名為消費的創造行為」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.09,0:15:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很像一個隱居網路的「個體」會得到的結論呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.60,0:15:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Stand Alone Complex嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.97,0:15:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好我對孤獨有堅強的抵抗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,系統之所以沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.74,0:15:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,認真評價我對社會的功勞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.98,0:15:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是因為我天生的資質造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.32,0:15:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我花了很多時間才注意到這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.12,0:15:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是對自己有自卑感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.76,0:15:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 存在本身就有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.86,0:15:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,社會上確實存在系統本身期盼的人格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.00,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人們渴望得到這種人格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.10,0:15:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是對這件事卻毫無自覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.74,0:15:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你滿意現在的自己嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.04,0:15:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比我預計的還要滿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.88,0:16:03.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靈魂必須由物理性身體反推而得證其存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.78,0:16:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道靈魂其實會隨身體變化而改變模樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.02,0:16:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.49,0:16:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前有個在革命當中找到自己存在意義的思想家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.16,0:16:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有實踐給我們看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.60,0:16:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是指Patrick Sylvestre嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.43,0:16:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也曾為他的思想傾倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我崇拜英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.51,0:16:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚至真心盼望得到讓大眾擁戴的非凡能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.71,0:16:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是應該位於眾人之上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.05,0:16:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個想法自從我懂事以來就存在我的心中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.18,0:16:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果身體雖然妨礙了這個想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.49,0:16:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命運卻站在我這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遇到生死懸於一線的事故後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.99,0:16:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的身體產生改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到靈魂也發生變化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.86,0:16:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像那位思想家因為遇到革命做出那些事情一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也被賦予使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.81,0:17:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將國家這個系統重新架構的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是國家改造論者?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.88,0:17:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者說是誇大妄想狂?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.45,0:17:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個國家現在所追求的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.02,0:17:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乃是只有透過消費第三者才能重現的世外桃源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.29,0:17:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前這個國家曾在偶然當中體驗過那樣的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.69,0:17:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有動機的人們至今仍然不自覺的想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.47,0:17:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想把那個給他們而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.57,0:17:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後藉此成為英雄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.14,0:17:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的我沒有那種願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.84,0:17:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的任務是製造那個英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有動機的人們殷切盼望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.32,0:17:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻不能大聲說出口的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.92,0:17:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是創造行動者來代言和實行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消費的結果所成立之世外桃源
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.69,0:17:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是指冷戰構造下的日本嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.00,0:18:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 誰是你製造的英雄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.81,0:18:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別的11人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.02,0:18:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 不妙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.13,0:18:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 快聯絡保安課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.06,0:18:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有電賊侵入了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比預計的還要晚來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.87,0:18:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 潛入被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.35,0:18:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 你所說的英雄的敵人是難民嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以他們為假想敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.85,0:18:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誘導國民的思想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.19,0:18:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.45,0:18:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,思想誘導應該是有必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.72,0:18:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了這個目的曲解法律也是必要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.53,0:19:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果會使得手段正當化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.80,0:19:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是恐怖主義和民主國家都通用的理論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.13,0:19:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,排除難民是國民的總體意志?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.90,0:19:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,含蓄是我國國民的美德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.84,0:19:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.47,0:19:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.74,0:19:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.64,0:19:17.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼看公安9課?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,9課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.25,0:19:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.18,0:19:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有來源的仇恨連鎖已經停不下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.82,0:19:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們將會在國民總體意志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.49,0:19:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及自身正義的夾縫之中苦惱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.23,0:19:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校 不快點離線會有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時間到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在到達6號出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,管區員警查問的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.01,0:19:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊威脅要自爆一邊逃進地下鐵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.29,0:19:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然要他們停下列車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.59,0:20:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是乘客仍在列車上車身大致上已經進入車站
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.66,0:20:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何一定要阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.66,0:20:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你走那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.94,0:20:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是難民沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.57,0:20:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.24,0:20:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好 就這樣別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.11,0:20:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩手放到頭後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣 我不會傷害你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.09,0:20:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢慢的 不要緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.11,0:20:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.85,0:21:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼開槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.65,0:21:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.36,0:21:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是信管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩叫救護車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.13,0:21:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為她肚子裏面有炸彈必須完全隔離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.70,0:21:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.02,0:21:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保安課的人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.02,0:21:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上清查建築物裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.69,0:21:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電賊似乎使用誘餌直接潛入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.99,0:21:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保安部員在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.53,0:21:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點再啟動SAT-MAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.00,0:21:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,檢查病毒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.70,0:21:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,防壁陣列再啟動之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.01,0:22:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的作業交給波賽頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.04,0:22:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會再出現在這裏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.38,0:22:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一件總算控制住了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.39,0:22:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差一點點就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.09,0:22:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 對今後還是有影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.79,0:22:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是難民發出的宣戰佈告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.66,0:22:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特的看法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.97,0:22:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很遺憾是正確的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.03,0:22:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別的11人恐怕就是合田製造的個別主義者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.31,0:22:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的是引發難民暴動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.11,0:22:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,訴求大概是暫時在這個國家建立他們的自治區吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.35,0:22:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到目前為止我們都是慘敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.55,0:22:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合田構思的仇恨連鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.29,0:22:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確實已經開始轉動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.51,0:23:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.25,0:23:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.76,0:23:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.73,0:23:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.03,0:23:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.57,0:23:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音--醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.64,0:23:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字--然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.14,0:23:44.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省視自身--醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.24,0:23:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我--時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.58,0:23:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.95,0:23:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的--它就在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.92,0:24:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在軀殼裏的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.39,0:24:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音--醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.40,0:24:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字--然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.47,0:24:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省視自身--醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.17,0:24:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我--時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.21,0:24:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.61,0:24:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去讓這一切成真的--它就在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.75,0:24:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在這個軀殼裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,

